nit: I think it is good to categorize all log messages. That is, each log message to have a category. That would be `BCLog::VALIDATION` in this case. The "Info" severity will ensure the message is logged unconditionally, regardless of whether it has category or not.

```diff
- LogInfo("%s\n", msg);
+ LogPrintLevel(BCLog::VALIDATION, BCLog::Level::Info, "%s", msg);
```

